{"tid":163922,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加決定留低：我20年來一直領軍列前4","createTime":"2017-03-20T10:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T11:53:01.000Z","uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2677a2243de3994efbc1be0f90baf42b750cdf1","tid":163922,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/1/351/17585878351/17584476329_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F1%2F351%2F17585878351%2F17584476329_600x399.jpg&h=dfabef01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=01fc04b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴領隊雲加出「廠」成定局？未必！英國傳媒稱他已決定留效。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴上周末不敵西布朗，錄得近5場英超第4場敗仗，領隊雲加賽後稱已為未來作出決定，言詞間暗示季尾可能離開執教逾20年的兵工廠，亦有報道指會方已擬定接棒者，其中多蒙特的杜慈乃熱門人選。不過，多份英國報章認為這位法國名帥未言退。英國《衛報》指阿仙奴董事局依然力撐雲加，即使球隊早前在歐聯被拜仁慕尼黑以總計10:2打敗，依然未動搖對雲加的支持，並會向他提供兩年新約。<br />\n<br />\n另外，《天空體育》亦引述雲加的言論，指他並不在意歐聯大敗：「我的決定不一定與它有關，因為我20年來一直領軍列前4，不會是近期的戰果決定我的意願。這不是世界末日。」<br />\n<br />\n上周末「兵」敗山楂球場，雲加全場都在噓聲中度過，有球迷租用兩架飛機盤旋球場上空，展示&ldquo;Wenger Out: No New Contract&rdquo;字句的橫額，而場內亦有高舉&ldquo;Wenger Out&rdquo;的橫額。<br />\n<br />\n經過新一輪英超後，阿仙奴27戰得50分跌至第6位，被周日贏波的曼聯超越。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp17585878351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp17585878351&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b32ac120\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp17585878351&h=89b30c11\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp17585878351</a>"},{"pid":"d26fe1b0b06370fe4be67e746cd7f3ddf7d47451","tid":163922,"uid":37902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:30:46.000Z","msg":"永續<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bb93411c59c57fae6edadc2b88325fae136b89","tid":163922,"uid":6728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:30:54.000Z","msg":"永續把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反雲都係留返啖氣暖肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a757989b8effc6b0d1507c02fe449efce4dd67","tid":163922,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:34:00.000Z","msg":"好撚型"},{"pid":"facb1f138f07f2cc0e87728cab5eb81706a7cf1e","tid":163922,"uid":66129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:35:41.000Z","msg":"支持永續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036e630561f8a02632dcbb00389a65bd750f1053","tid":163922,"uid":26931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:47:40.000Z","msg":"所以今年咪跌出囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fca8b3e14bfb56bc6e26f81a68e239ab5221300","tid":163922,"uid":3832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:48:09.000Z","msg":"永續雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n迷雲又然一場"},{"pid":"444ff300f3858ca95e24ec24b7a79c7d71e40488","tid":163922,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:48:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以今年咪跌出囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n季尾會發力"},{"pid":"73f30164f0a1cf0182cca63b27964a4cf6828dca","tid":163922,"uid":12154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"永續雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 